Text: How do i add them to msn??

logon to your msn. go to "tools." choose "my msn smilyes" or something like that. then click on the option at top right corner... or with short-cut command (C). Sorry i had msn in different language. i think the rest of the steps are quite self-explanatory, as long as u know where your bt downloads are. good luck.
Thanks to yukimura0224 for the assist
